/static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho, Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo tr\u00ean tay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng &ldquo;Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo;</h2>\r\nPaul Pogba l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. N\u00e0o l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 4 ng\u00e0y sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8, n\u00e0o l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u \u0111i v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u00ea. Nh\u01b0 HLV Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 60 ph\u00fat. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t 84 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Paul-Pogba-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester-da-toa-sang-ruc-ro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Antonio Valencia, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19. Ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 qu\u00ean \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd Pogba l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i hay \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. N\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i g\u1ecdi Pogba l\u00e0 &ldquo;m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo;. Anh di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ea3 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 penalty ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU 2-1 Leicester B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU 2-1 Leicester B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/MU-2-1-Leicester-Bong-dang-Sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester l\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ch\u00ea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez, b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Wes Morgan song v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eadp tr\u00fang tay c\u1ee7a Daniel Amartey. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Andre Marriner ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng v\u1edbi Sanchez, Pogba l\u0129nh tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 11m. Anh thong dong, \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u01b0a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn Pogba ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Anh t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00ean l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i M.U c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Leicester c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t&rdquo; ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: &ldquo;Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo;</span><br>\r\n<span>Paul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMay m\u00e0 c\u00f3 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, M.U ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 cho Leicester l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn hi\u1ec7p 1. Nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a David de Gea, l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i rung l\u00ean sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a James Maddison.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho \u1edf b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 v\u1ebb lo l\u1eafng khi M.U b\u1ecb Leicester l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt. \u00d4ng c\u00e0ng b\u1ef1c b\u1ed9i h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn phung ph\u00ed nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Romelu Lukaku khi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Schmeichel d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho va Pogba\" title=\"Mourinho va Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Mourinho-va-Pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t Pogba</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may l\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Pogba, M.U \u0111\u00e3 v\u1edbt v\u00e1t l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. H\u1ecd ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 6 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 83, Luke Shaw kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Juan Mata n\u00e2ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u00ean 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ra ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 hoan ngh\u00eanh nhi\u1ec7t li\u1ec7t t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Mourinho d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i v\u1ed7 vai nh\u1eb9 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng khai r\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" title=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Pogba-toa-sang-giup-M.U-ha-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Leicester tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-1. M.U kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 bao, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xoay chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 Pogba hay Alexis Sanchez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U, Pogba ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1eabn tinh th\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t &ldquo;Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Thong-tin-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&amp;autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2230","checkdouble":"194228"},{"date":"08:13 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Aston Villa vs Wigan 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-aston-villa-vs-wigan-21h00-ngay-118-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Derby County vs Leeds l\u00fac 23h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Leeds 23h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Leeds 23h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Derby-County-vs-Leeds.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Derby County vs Leeds</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Derby County vs Leeds: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Trong kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho Derby County trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leeds. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2005, Derby County th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn 9/12 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leeds tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pride Park (thua 1). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Derby County t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Frank Lampard to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 5 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ghi 13 b\u00e0n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Derby County \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Reading v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Pride Park c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lampard. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leeds Utd v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. D\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a HLV c\u00e1o gi\u00e0 Marcelo Bielsa, The Whites v\u1eeba c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec1-pa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u201cng\u1ecdt\u201d h\u01a1n, khi h\u1ea1 knock-out Stoke City (\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb Premier League) 3-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 TLCA, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 2). Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn phe kh\u00e1ch.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 83 tr\u1eadn, Derby County th\u1eafng 33, h\u00f2a 16, thua 34.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Derby County, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 22, h\u00f2a 9, thua 11. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nDerby County: Chris Martin (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Ikechi Anya (kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn).\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\nLeeds Utd: \u0110\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2229","checkdouble":"194229"},{"date":"08:16 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea (21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa c\u00f9ng Sarriball","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Sarri. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2017/18.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nChelsea trong l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-2 t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Man City &ldquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rdquo; k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian sa th\u1ea3i Conte, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 mua \u0111\u1eaft b\u00e1n r\u1ebb, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Chelsea \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi thu n\u1ea1p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 Kepa v\u00e0 Kovacic, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi tri\u1ec3n &ldquo;Sarriball&rdquo; &ndash; chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda m\u00e0 Napoli t\u1eebng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, l\u00e0m quen chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 Man City c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, l\u00e0m quen l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadt may cho Sarri, khi \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Thibaut Courtois, v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh Jorginho &ndash; c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t may cho Sarri, khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng Huddersfield, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec The Blues \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nHuddersfield kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a David Wagner \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean &ldquo;to\u00e0n m\u1ea1ng&rdquo;. Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Kirklees.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd thua t\u1edbi 10 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2018, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Terriers tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 2 l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Huddersfield v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Preview Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1182018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV David Wagner c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a The Blues, m\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft, Huddersfield &ldquo;s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c duy nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Chelsea c\u0169ng thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Burnley &ndash; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o h\u00e0ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Chelsea vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/chelsea1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea th\u1eafng Huddersfield 3-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hudderfield kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Chelsea 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hudderfield th\u1eafng Chelsea tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 64 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2 trong 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield thua 10 tr\u1eadn, ki\u1ebfm v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 &ndash; \u00edt h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8, nh\u01b0ng 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Huddersfield \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc (3-1, 1-1)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong 19 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic v\u00e0 Kepa trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Courtois, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Caballero s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Sarri, v\u1edbi Luiz &ndash; Rudier l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Hazard v\u00e0 Willian b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Danny Williams, Erik D\u1ee7m v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Juninho Bacuna.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1&nbsp;Huddersfield vs Chelsea: 1-2</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Top 4, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0a The Blues tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\">HLV Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Hazard</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, d\u1eadp t\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n anh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2228","checkdouble":"194230"},{"date":"08:37 11/08","title":"Pogba n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester</span> trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Paul-Pogba-phat-bieu-ve-MU-sau-chien-thang-truoc-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 91 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 68 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 54 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, 6 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, 2 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, 2 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Pogba, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" title=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o sau World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft tay ngay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Mourinho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho CLB, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2227","checkdouble":"194231"},{"date":"08:20 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Leeds 23h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-derby-county-vs-leeds-23h30-ngay-118-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Derby County vs Leeds l\u00fac 23h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Leeds 23h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Leeds 23h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Derby-County-vs-Leeds.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Derby County vs Leeds</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Derby County vs Leeds: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Trong kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho Derby County trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leeds. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2005, Derby County th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn 9/12 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leeds tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pride Park (thua 1). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Derby County t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Frank Lampard to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 5 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ghi 13 b\u00e0n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Derby County \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Reading v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Pride Park c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lampard. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leeds Utd v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. D\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a HLV c\u00e1o gi\u00e0 Marcelo Bielsa, The Whites v\u1eeba c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec1-pa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u201cng\u1ecdt\u201d h\u01a1n, khi h\u1ea1 knock-out Stoke City (\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb Premier League) 3-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 TLCA, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 2). Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn phe kh\u00e1ch.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 83 tr\u1eadn, Derby County th\u1eafng 33, h\u00f2a 16, thua 34.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Derby County, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 22, h\u00f2a 9, thua 11. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nDerby County: Chris Martin (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Ikechi Anya (kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn).\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\nLeeds Utd: \u0110\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2226","checkdouble":"194232"},{"date":"08:49 11/08","title":"HLV Claude Puel gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Leicester th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-giai-thich-ly-do-tai-sao-leicester-that-bai-truoc-mu.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 56 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a M.U, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Claude Puel \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tham v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Leicester b\u1ecb gi\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Claude-Puel-phat-bieu-ve-tran-MU-vs-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Sanchez \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang tay m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Leicester trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, M.U ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Leicester c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh David de Gea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuke Shaw v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho M.U, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Leicester d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Vardy \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThua tr\u1eadn 1-2, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho d\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Puel ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Leicester thua tr\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 56 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claude Puel phat bieu ve tran MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-giai-thich-ly-do-tai-sao-leicester-that-bai-truoc-mu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Leicester g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2225","checkdouble":"194233"},{"date":"08:45 11/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eabn \"ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh\" so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-van-chua-du-trinh-so-sanh-voi-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2></h2>\u00a0</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2224","checkdouble":"194234"},{"date":"08:58 11/08","title":"Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh pen v\u1edbi Sanchez","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/bo-doi-ngoi-sao-se-quyet-dinh-thanh-bai-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City \u2013 \u201c\u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d c\u1ee7a Man United, Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPogba g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Sanchez<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i Premier League, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc The Foxes. H\u1ecd s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alexis Sanchez khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00f9ng tay ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, nh\u01b0ng Pogba m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Chile, nh\u1eb1m nh\u1eadn l\u1ea5y qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra. Pogba c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eafc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m penalty th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn l\u1ea5y n\u00f3. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t cho Alexis. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez\" title=\"Pogba thuc hien thanh cong penalty cho M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Claude-Puel-phat-bieu-ve-tran-MU-vs-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi quay l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. T\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tham gia v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u&rdquo; &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t scandal nh\u01b0 Neymar &ndash; Cavani. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, Mourinho c\u0169ng trao cho Pogba chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Thong-tin-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&amp;autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-tran-mu-21-leicester-bong-dang-sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-172-194228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-tran-mu-21-leicester-bong-dang-sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-172-194228.html\">M.U 2-1 Leicester: B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng &ldquo;Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho, Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: &ldquo;Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2223","checkdouble":"194235"},{"date":"08:40 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Birmingham 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-middlesbrough-vs-birmingham-21h00-ngay-118-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Middlesbrough vs Birmingham l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 3 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Birmingham 21h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Middlesbrough vs Birmingham 21h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Middlesbrough-vs-Birmingham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Middlesbrough vs Birmingham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Middlesbrough vs Birmingham: 0-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Middlesbrough thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 5 chung cy\u1ed9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh. Ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng play-off gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Premier League. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tony Pulis \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 su\u00f4n s\u1ebb khi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u1edbi \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay, Boro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong Middlesbrough ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Birmingham. Phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Tony Pulis kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 (Aden Flint v\u00e0 Paddy McNair). Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf chi\u1ec1u \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Riverside \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t 2 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Patrick Bamford (t\u1edbi Leeds) v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao tr\u1ebb Barca, Adama Traore chuy\u1ec3n sang t\u00e2n binh Premier League, Wolves.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1edfi v\u1eady, Boro \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Birmingham ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i n\u00e0y. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 5/6 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Middlesbrough b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 8 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Birmingham g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 4).<br>\r\n- 5/6 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- Middlesbrough th\u1eafng 7/9 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Birmingham g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- Middlesbrough: V\u1eafng Rudy Gestede (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Daniel Ayala c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.<br>\r\n- Birmingham: Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a David Stockdale c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2222","checkdouble":"194237"},{"date":"23:36 10/08","title":"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd \u2018Messi m\u1edbi\u2019, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/phot-lo-messi-moi-olympic-indonesia-trieu-tap-sao-u40-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Olympic Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Messi m\u1edbi, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Messi m\u1edbi, Olympic Indonesia tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp sao U40 d\u1ef1 ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/XT5gRGy6Ah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Alberto Goncalves l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n\u00a0Olympic Indonesia t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 V\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alberto Goncalves, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 38 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alberto Goncalves l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c Brazil. Anh \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Indonesia trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sriwijaya. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 6 l\u1ea7n 'khai h\u1ecfa'.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Alberto Goncalves \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Alberto Goncalves, m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c H\u00e0 Lan, Stefano Lilipaly v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Andritany Ardiyasa. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a \"Messi m\u1edbi\" Egy Maulana Vikri.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, Indonesia n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i Palestine, Hong Kong (TQ), \u0110\u00e0i B\u1eafc Trung Hoa v\u00e0 L\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2221","checkdouble":"194209"},{"date":"23:55 10/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/truyen-thong-nhat-ban-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang theo s\u00e1t t\u1eebng \u2018\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i, n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u01b0\u1edbc\u2019 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.</h2><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c v\u1eeba l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i Asiad 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal, Olympic Pakistan. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc c\u0169ng xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Truyen-thong-Nhat-Ban-noi-gi-ve-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 t\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u1eddi gian qua. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qoly c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd n\u00e0y m\u00f4 t\u1ea3: \"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi m\u00e0 trong tay HLV Hajime th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Olympic 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 v\u1ecb \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m nay. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u1ecd\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Qoly vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 hai ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 sau: \u00a0\u201cTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf K-League. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i J-League 2 nh\u01b0ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18-168-194207.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/10/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18-168-194207.html\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194206.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad-168-194206.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2220","checkdouble":"194210"},{"date":"23:56 10/08","title":"Alexis Sanchez tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 n\u1eeda n\u0103m kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 \u1edf Old Trafford","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/alexis-sanchez-trai-long-ve-nua-nam-khon-kho-o-old-trafford.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pogba trong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd do m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Pogba trong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- MU: Pogba 3' (pen), Shaw 83'<br>\r\n- Leicester City: Vardy 90'+2<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nMan Utd: </strong>De Gea; Darmian, Bailly,  Lindelof, Shaw; Pogba (Fellaini 84'), A Pereira, Fred (McTominay 76');  Mata,  Rashford (Lukaku 67'), Sanchez.<br>\r\n<strong>Leicester:</strong> Schmeichel; Ricardo, Morgan, Maguire, Chilwell. Amartey (Ghezzal 63'), Silva,  Ndidi, Maddison (Vardy 63'), Gray, Iheanacho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2219","checkdouble":"194211"},{"date":"00:26 11/08","title":"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/12/hlv-truong-clb-thai-son-nam-noi-gi-khi-vao-chung-ket-futsal-cac-clb-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, HLV Miguel Rodrigo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m 6-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Lebanon, Bank of Beirut.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft futsal ch\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/12/tan-hlv-miguel-rodrigo-futsal-viet-nam-van-thua-thai-lan.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miguel Rodrigo t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn 3-1 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam ch\u01a1i b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh v\u00e0 ghi li\u1ec1n 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Qu\u1ed1c H\u01b0ng (29') v\u00e0 c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Th\u00e0nh T\u00edn (32', 35' v\u00e0 36') gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 5-3. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 6-5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u1ede c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2015 v\u00e0 2017 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Miguel Rodrigo, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T futsal Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 cho hay: \"T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 3-1. S\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p CLB \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Iran, Mes Sungun Varzaghan. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CLB Nafit Al-wasat 3-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h ng\u00e0y 12/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight: Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam 6-5 Beirut<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/10/Thai-Son-Nam-FC-6-5-Bank-of-Beirut.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2218","checkdouble":"194214"},{"date":"06:46 11/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/21/Tien-dao-Michy-Batshuayi-Co-hoi-cuoi-cung-hinh-anh-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01a1i\u201d Michy Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d Valencia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41);\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Antonio Conte tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Michy Batshuayi lang b\u1ea1t sang \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh thu\u00ea cho Borussia Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 9 b\u00e0n/14 tr\u1eadn.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/21/Tien-dao-Michy-Batshuayi-Co-hoi-cuoi-cung-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi r\u1eddi Chelsea gia nh\u1eadp Valencia theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi Chelsea hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ra h\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Olivier Giroud \u0111\u1ebfn Alvaro Morata. Kh\u00f4ng, s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Batshuayi r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c khi anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Chelsea l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Valencia theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb CLB th\u00e0nh London nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t video clip \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i n\u1ed9i dung v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e0n d\u01a1i. \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01a1i\u201d (Batman) l\u00e0 bi\u1ec7t danh c\u1ee7a Batshuayi, trong khi Valencia l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Batshuayi \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a t\u00e2n HLV Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho hai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Tammy Abraham v\u00e0 Callum Hudson-Odoi, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng trung phong \u0111\u00e0n anh kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Giroud v\u00e0 Morata.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay, Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2217","checkdouble":"194218"}]}